# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Shift_Elite DB — Frontend Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Set this to your Railway C++ backend URL for production.
# Leave unset (or remove the line) for local dev — Vite will
# proxy /api → localhost:8080 automatically via vite.config.ts.
#
# Example:
# VITE_API_URL=https://shift-elite-db.up.railway.app/api
VITE_API_URL=
